{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-js","path":"/post/ghost-parade-anime-expo-2018/","result":{"data":{"wordpressPost":{"title":"Ghost Parade, Game Indonesia Yang Buat Kejutan di Anime Expo 2018","content":"<p>Bulan Juli ini seakan jadi bulan yang sibuk dalam skena game Indonesia. Para <em>developer</em> game lokal tak hanya disibukkan dengan pagelaran BEKRAF Game Prime 2018. Beberapa <em>developer</em> pun bersiap-siap dengan perilisan game mereka di luar Indonesia.</p>\n<p>Setelah Agate merilis <a href=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/valthirian-arc-hero-school-story-switch-ps4-pc/\">Valthirian Arc: Hero School Story</a> bersama <em>publisher</em> PQube dan Toge Productions melepas Ultra Space Battle Brawl di Nintendo Switch, kini giliran <em>developer</em> Lentera Nusantara yang unjuk gigi. Tak tanggung-tanggung, mereka terbang ke Los Angeles untuk mengenalkan game terbaru mereka, Ghost Parade.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><iframe style=\"border: none; overflow: hidden;\" src=\"https://www.facebook.com/plugins/video.php?href=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FGhostParadeGame%2Fvideos%2F784417465101016%2F&amp;show_text=0&amp;width=560\" width=\"560\" height=\"315\" frameborder=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\"></iframe></p>\n<p>Ghost Parade menjadi salah satu game yang dikenalkan oleh <em>publisher</em> Aksys Games dalam panel mereka di Anime Expo 2018 pada tanggal 7 Juli 2018 lalu. Aksys merupakan <em>publisher</em> yang menerbitkan beberapa game Jepang populer seperti Guilty Gear, Blazblue, Record of Agarest War, dan masih banyak lagi.</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_49097\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-49097\" data-attachment-id=\"49097\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/ghost-parade-anime-expo-2018/attachment/01-ghost-parade/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/01-ghost-parade.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"01-ghost-parade\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/01-ghost-parade-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/01-ghost-parade.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-49097\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/01-ghost-parade.jpg\" alt=\"ghost parade\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/01-ghost-parade.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/01-ghost-parade-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-49097\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Sumber: Playtoko</p></div>\n<p>Ghost Parade mengisahkan petualangan Suri yang tersesat di hutan dan mencoba untuk mencari jalan pulang. Dalam game <em>platformer</em> 2D ini, Suri akan bertemu dengan berbagai hantu yang membantunya pulang ke rumah. Suri pun harusmembantu para hantu menyelamatkan hutan dari campur tangan manusia rakus.</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_49098\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-49098\" data-attachment-id=\"49098\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/ghost-parade-anime-expo-2018/attachment/02-ghost-parade/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/02-ghost-parade.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"02-ghost-parade\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/02-ghost-parade-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/02-ghost-parade.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-49098\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/02-ghost-parade.jpg\" alt=\"Sumber: Lentera Nuasntara\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/02-ghost-parade.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/02-ghost-parade-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-49098\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Sumber: Lentera Nuasntara</p></div>\n<p>“Saya senang atas perilisan Ghost Parade di seluruh dunia dalam berbagai macam <em>platform</em>, ini seperti mimpi yang menjadi nyata apalagi bekerjasama dengan Aksys Games yang sudah mengeluarkan judul-judul populer seperti Blazblue,” ungkap CEO Lentera Nusantara, Azizah Assatari.</p>\n<p>“Kami juga sangat bahagia dengan tanggapan positif orang-orang di Anime Expo 2018 yang menyambut antusias game ini. Harapan kami mudah-mudahan Ghost Parade dapat membawa budaya lokal Nusantara ke seluruh dunia dan mengharumkan nama Indonesia!” tambahnya.</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_49099\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-49099\" data-attachment-id=\"49099\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/ghost-parade-anime-expo-2018/attachment/03-ghost-parade/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/03-ghost-parade.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"03-ghost-parade\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/03-ghost-parade-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/03-ghost-parade.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-49099\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/03-ghost-parade.jpg\" alt=\"Sumber: Steam\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/03-ghost-parade.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/03-ghost-parade-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-49099\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Sumber: Steam</p></div>\n<p>Ghost Parade akan segera rilis untuk berbagai <em>platform</em> dan konsol game populer seperti PS4, Nintendo Switch, dan PC melalui Steam. Kalau kamu penasaran dengan gamenya, kamu bisa cek <em>fanpage</em> Facebook mereka untuk informasi lebih lanjut. Jangan lupa untuk <em>book</em> tiket gratis kamu di <a href=\"http://bit.ly/bgp2018\">bit.ly/bgp2018</a>.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><iframe src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/h-OoWCpdgTM\" width=\"640\" height=\"360\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\"></iframe></p>\n"}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"id":"c5d1e91e-07d9-5ade-868b-0ee0be43680b"}}}